# Copy to .dev.vars (gitignored) and fill in for local builds/deploys.
#
# GITHUB_TOKEN is used ONLY at build time, by the three fetch scripts behind
# scripts/build-resume.sh: gen-resume-source.mjs, gen-projects-data.mjs, and
# gen-blog-data.mjs. Use a fine-grained personal access token with read-only
# "Contents" + "Metadata" permission, scoped to the repos named in config/.
# Never expose it to the client — it is only read by the Node build scripts,
# never bundled into the site.
#
# The resume fetch is REQUIRED: without a token the build fails there. Projects
# and blog are best-effort and fall back to the committed lib/projects-data.json
# and lib/posts-data.json.
GITHUB_TOKEN=
